'From Squeak3.8alpha of ''17 July 2004'' [latest update: #5987] on 16 September 2004 at 5:07:27 pm'!!SpaceTally methodsFor: 'class analysis' stamp: 'KLC 9/16/2004 16:59'!systemWideSpaceTally	"Answer a collection of SpaceTallyItems representing the memory space (in bytes) consumed 	by the code and instances of each class in the system. Note that code sizes do not currently 	report memory consumed by class variables. "	"(SpaceTally new systemWideSpaceTally asSortedCollection: [:a :b | a spaceForInstances > b spaceForInstances]) asArray"	self preAllocateResultsFor: Smalltalk allClasses.	Smalltalk garbageCollect.	self computeSpaceUsage.	^ results! !